# Dataset Analysis - Oxford Flowers 102

## Introduction
This project analyzes a public dataset to understand its structure and characteristics. The Oxford Flowers 102 dataset is used.

## Objective
- Explore dataset structure
- Analyze number of classes and images
- Visualize images with labels

## Dataset
Oxford Flowers 102 dataset contains:
- 102 flower categories
- Around 8000+ images

## Methodology
- Loaded dataset using torchvision
- Checked dataset size and classes
- Displayed sample images

## Output
The dataset was successfully analyzed and visualized.

## Conclusion
Understanding dataset structure helps in building better machine learning models.
